parameters: \nc<>Ku, o, oooo...! Not yet, I'm not done yet...!

\nc<>It's impossible. If you rely any further on this dark
power, you will be consumed by the power itself. Surrender
quietly.

\nc<>Don't make me laugh. Just when I can finally see a shining
and bright future ahead, when I finally became capable of
doing something!

\nc<>Are you telling me to go back to the time when I was
incompetent and pathetic...?!

\nc<>I'm not telling you to go back, I'm telling you to start
over! The old you was not insignificant at all.
\nc<>Look, there are people here waiting for you like this!
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]I was worried because they said it was a health issue.");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]Why are you doing something like being a villain??");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]I was really saved by the advice I received.");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]Surprisingly, there are a lot of people who know about it, right?");

\nc<>...Kuu! To dig up someone's dark history... So, what is this
all about?

\nc<>A couple of fans cheering won't change anything, this
industry isn't that sweet and sugary!

\nc<>If I lose the power of the monster, everyone will turn their
backs on me and leave!
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]It was a muscular muscle video, but...");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]Its not a hardcore game, you know.");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]Matsuos video successfully achieved a 10 kilogram weight loss.");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]I dont even watch workout videos in the first place.");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]But Matsuo, they usually listen well to what I have to say.");
\nc<>Shut up... I told you to erase it, you piece of shit...!

\nc<>Therefore, it may be true that without the power of a
villain, you can't become popular.

\nc<>But, what you had wasn't just that. The effort you made for
the fans wasn't in vain.

\nc<>Alright, I'll admit that what you're saying is correct. So,
what the hell is it then?

\nc<>Did you forget because your head is in the clouds? I'm a
villain, you know?

\nc<>When I reveal my true identity, my life as a streamer will
be over!

\nc<>It would have been better if I had just killed you like
that. Then, I could have disappeared without knowing hope.

\nc<>To think that there was potential in me, that my efforts
weren't meaningless... to say something like that now...
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]Do you think its unforgivable by any chance?");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]I always get beaten up by Levantia.");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]I only have an image in my mind.");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]I used to do it a lot when I was in middle school.");

\nc<>Do you, by any chance, think of yourself as a tremendous
villain? No, you were quite strong though.
\nc<>Basically, you've always been defeated by me, haven't you?

\nc<>Of course, it's not good to appear in the city and cause a
rampage... but I can assert that I am a magical girl.

\nc<>The crime you committed is not at a level that can never be
undone.
\nc<>By the way, this is completely unrelated, but...

\nc<>There's a rumor that there's someone who desperately
protected the citizens so that someone wouldn't make a
decisive mistake.
\nc<>Your actions... were not just meddling, but also right...

\nc<>Levantia, turns out they're the type to hold grudges,
meow...
\nc<>What should I do from now on...?

\nc<>I don't know about that. Even though I said that, I can't
say for sure if it will sell again.

\nc<>In the end, I think the only thing you can do is believe in
yourself and work hard until the end.
\nc<>I obtained the memory M4: Black Muscle Extermination.

\nc<>Good listeners increased by 7,000, while bad listeners
increased by 3,000.
